      <title>特朗普和哈里斯以超出预算的税收提案争夺选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/harris-vs-trump-tax-cuts-take-spotlight-in-battle-to-win-swing-state-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯正在进行一场税收政策竞赛，互相抄袭和超越对方的提案，以期在华盛顿即将爆发的税法修改之战之前争取关键战场州的投票集团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/harris-vs-trump-tax-cuts-take-spotlight-in-battle-to-win-swing-state-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 15:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰与美国签署价值 100 亿美元的阿帕奇直升机合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/poland-signs-10-billion-deal-with-us-for-apache-helicopters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着华沙加强其防御能力，波兰签署了一项价值 100 亿美元的协议，从美国制造商波音公司购买近一百架 AH-64E 阿帕奇攻击直升机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/poland-signs-10-billion-deal-with-us-for-apache-helicopters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>UAW 起诉特朗普和马斯克，称他们在 X 采访中恐吓工人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/trump-musk-hit-with-uaw-labor-charge-over-streaming-interview</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全美汽车工人联合会对前总统唐纳德·特朗普和亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克提出了不公平劳工行为指控，称这两人在周一晚间接受 X 采访时非法恐吓工人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/trump-musk-hit-with-uaw-labor-charge-over-streaming-interview</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:33:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Mpox 宣布非洲卫生紧急状态以指挥应对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/africa-cdc-calls-mpox-health-emergency-to-help-marshal-resources</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲迅速蔓延的猪瘟疫情被宣布为非洲大陆的公共卫生紧急事件，该地区的主要卫生咨询机构在调动资源时首次动用了这一权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/africa-cdc-calls-mpox-health-emergency-to-help-marshal-resources</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非改革部门将重点关注地方政府和住房</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/south-african-reform-unit-to-focus-on-local-government-housing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统府和国家财政部设立的“Vulindlela 行动”部门旨在加速结构性改革、促进经济增长，该部门将把重点转向振兴市镇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/south-african-reform-unit-to-focus-on-local-government-housing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:14:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安娜·温图尔 (Anna Wintour) 和托里·伯奇 (Tory Burch) 将在汉普顿为哈里斯举办募捐活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/anna-wintour-tory-burch-to-host-hamptons-fundraiser-for-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府商务部长吉娜·雷蒙多 (Gina Raimondo) 是一些华尔街巨头的宠儿，她将在劳动节周末帮助副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 筹集资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/anna-wintour-tory-burch-to-host-hamptons-fundraiser-for-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 13:40:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰密谋入侵，让克里姆林宫失去平衡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ukraine-plotted-cross-border-attack-to-throw-kremlin-off-balance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位了解袭击计划的西方官员透露，乌克兰在上周强行越过边境之前，一直在考虑发动袭击的几种可能性，这些袭击将震惊莫斯科领导层，并使总统弗拉基米尔·普京陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ukraine-plotted-cross-border-attack-to-throw-kremlin-off-balance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 13:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰入侵后，俄罗斯军队短缺问题暴露无遗，新一轮征兵风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ukraine-kursk-incursion-exposes-russia-troop-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰战争中士兵短缺问题日益严重，俄罗斯不得不提高征兵奖金，以避免再次出现不受欢迎的征兵行动。到目前为止，这一举措似乎没有起到什么作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ukraine-kursk-incursion-exposes-russia-troop-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:13:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈西娜下台后孟加拉国暴力事件引发印度教少数群体恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-13/the-spasm-of-violence-in-bangladesh-after-hasina-s-ouster-stirs-fear-within-country-s-hindu-minority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国库尔纳（美联社）——上周，一场大规模起义迫使孟加拉国长期执政的总理下台并逃离该国，一位曾为其政党工作的 65 岁退休审计员担心自己的生命安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-13/the-spasm-of-violence-in-bangladesh-after-hasina-s-ouster-stirs-fear-within-country-s-hindu-minority</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 05:11:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戈特海默呼吁为火车乘客补偿延误费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/nj-congressman-calls-for-rail-riders-to-be-reimbursed-for-delays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年夏天，纽约市地区的通勤者在火车和站台上被困数小时之久，导致美国铁路公司服务中断，从而导致新泽西州交通乘客长时间延误，一名美国议员希望新泽西州交通局对乘客进行补偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/nj-congressman-calls-for-rail-riders-to-be-reimbursed-for-delays</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 17:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
